{"tid":736884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[HK No IT]1300表格未電子化智慧政府淪空談","createTime":"2018-07-10T14:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T15:57:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5224ecac2fcffcad9812fb1f052586da64335a88","tid":736884,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"政府於去年底公布《香港智慧城市藍圖》，計劃把香港打造成「智慧城市」，藍圖內其中一個範疇為「智慧政府」，在多個部門內開發不同資訊科技系統向市民提供服務發展為「電子政府」，但外界一直批評電子政府進度緩慢。昨日在立法會相關事務委員會會議上，多名立法會議員不滿政府電子服務，批評政府網頁介面落後、指示不清晰，甚至突然Hang機（停機），更有逾一千三百款表格未電子化，與會的官員亦承認現有的情況不理想，會按程序轉變及適時檢討。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180710/00176_028.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180710%2F00176_028.html&d=eR1TBwj6C9DhNxCubXnTRghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=4b96e162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180710/00176_028.html</a>"},{"pid":"675968ac2a2565b2296a8d2312b57c8490aa4bc5","tid":736884,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:41:07.000Z","msg":"HK No ??"},{"pid":"aa1b0d9676a2dc9e00b696e4fbf03611e4b1509f","tid":736884,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:44:58.000Z","msg":"申請老綜有冇電子化? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420536820cf0ad3bfd928466f0bdfeee877c0b2b","tid":736884,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa1b0d9676a2dc9e00b696e4fbf03611e4b1509f","tid":736884,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:44:58.000Z","msg":"申請老綜有冇電子化? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"b41672e5f276401d9fb9d1ccd7a93c6d1b4f2449","tid":736884,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"420536820cf0ad3bfd928466f0bdfeee877c0b2b","tid":736884,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,